data.description: Nice 3 bedroom, 2 baths, single story house in private lake community. Beautifully tiled floors in hallways, living room and family room, and recently carpeted bedrooms.  Remodeled kitchen with the state of the art oven, stove and microwave. Located within walking distance of Endeavor School of Exploration elementary school and Lakeview Leadership Academy middle school. You will get to enjoy a 200-acre private lake perfect for water sports, a beautiful private beach area for sunbathing & swimming plus 14 fishing areas and pier for the avid angler. The community center and private parks and ballfields provide a hub for social gatherings and activities, while the 24-hour security patrol ensures peace of mind. Access Spring Valley Lake Equestrian Center for equine boarding, events, and equestrian trails. If you're looking to elevate your lifestyle, joining the Bear Valley Country Club inside Spring Valley Lake is an enticing option. Here, you can indulge in the challenging 18-hole Robert Trent Jones championship golf course, play tennis, pickle ball or racquetball, work out in the fitness center, take a refreshing swim in the Olympic sized swimming pool or relax in the jacuzzi or sauna.  Gorgeous front lawn, huge backyard area with patio for relaxing with friends and family with a two car attached garage. Reach out for a private showing!
